   P_{1j}\,x_1 + P_{2j}\,x_2 + \dots + P_{mj}\,x_m = x_j \,. 
   \begin{bmatrix}       P_{11} & P_{21} & \dots & P_{m1} \\      P_{12} & P_{22} & \dots & P_{m2} \\      \vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots \\      P_{1m} & P_{2m} & \dots & P_{mm}   \end{bmatrix}   \begin{bmatrix} x_1 \\ x_2 \\ \vdots \\ x_m \end{bmatrix} =    \begin{bmatrix} x_1 \\ x_2 \\ \vdots \\ x_m \end{bmatrix}   
